S. African Veterans May Cost 65 Billion Rand, Business Day Says

-- B y   G o r d o n   B e l l
-- 
2011-03-07T05:41:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-07/s-african-veterans-may-cost-65-billion-rand-business-day-says.html
South African military veterans of
the fight against apartheid may cost the government20 billion
rand to 65 billion rand in benefit payments, Business Day
reported, citing a cost estimate by Alexander Forbes.  Legislation to compensate the veterans is being considered
by Parliament, the Johannesburg-based newspaper reported.   Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
